1
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:15,239
My Lord, don't worry.

2
00:01:15,239 --> 00:01:16,040
I'm watching her.

3
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,560
I'll take action as soon as she comes out.

4
00:01:18,079 --> 00:01:18,879
Got it, My Lord.

5
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:26,359
Miss Jiang, your luggage.

6
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:29,680
It's a bit chilly today.

7
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,159
I've prepared a coat for you.

8
00:01:31,159 --> 00:01:32,120
I hope you'll take it.

9
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:33,840
Thank you.

10
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:34,920
I've also packed

11
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,680
your personal items into the pocket.

12
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,400
Hope you have a pleasant stay.

13
00:01:41,359 --> 00:01:42,799
Personal items?

14
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,120
It's me.

15
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,159
Don't panic.

16
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:35,800
Listen to me.

17
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:37,719
I've found a safe place.

18
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,080
My Lord.

19
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,039
The woman surnamed Jiang hasn't gone out all day.

20
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:10,400
She's been taken to a safe place.

21
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,360
We have no chance to make a move.

22
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,159
Xiaohua, are you feeling better?

23
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,879
I brought you some dim sum.

24
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:34,680
Senior, sorry.

25
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:37,240
I didn't help you much this time.

26
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,560
You've helped me a lot.

27
00:03:39,879 --> 00:03:41,639
The successor restorer will be here soon.

28
00:03:42,639 --> 00:03:44,120
Let me take you back to the hotel.

29
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,680
No, thanks.

30
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:50,280
I have something to go out for.

31
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:52,240
I want to visit the place

32
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,639
where my ancestors lived before going back to Rongzhou.

33
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,479
Then send me the address.

34
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:58,039
I'll ask the driver to pick us up.

35
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,960
No, no need.

36
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:01,919
I'll go by myself.

37
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,120
You go on with your work.

38
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,360
Xunxun,

39
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:12,680
let me know before you go back to Rongzhou.

40
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:14,840
I'll take you to the airport.

41
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,439
Okay.

42
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:29,879
As long as she gives back the jade pendant,

43
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,319
don't let her suffer.

44
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,920
Hi, Miss Jiang.

45
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,680
Boss Ke asked me to show you around.

46
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:52,759
Get in the car.

47
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:55,480
I just remembered I left something here.

48
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,120
Leave me alone. Go ahead.

49
00:05:06,639 --> 00:05:07,560
Old classmate.

50
00:05:07,759 --> 00:05:10,319
Let's talk about the cooperation between Shen Group and the foundation.

51
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,439
No problem.

52
00:05:12,439 --> 00:05:13,279
Please come in.

53
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,079
Shen Shutu.

54
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,879
Answer the phone.

55
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:43,839
Hello?

56
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:45,160
Someone is following me.

57
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:45,920
Where are you?

58
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,759
I'll come to you.

59
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:47,839
Drinking in Zhonghuan?

60
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,560
It's too crowded.

61
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,560
Maybe next time.

62
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:52,120
You want me to go to Zhonghuan?

63
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,519
I have something to do now.

64
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,600
I'll come to you later.

65
00:05:57,959 --> 00:06:00,160
Young Master Shen, you're all dressed up.

66
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,319
Are you going on a date

67
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,920
or to handle some business?

68
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,360
I did have something to do,

69
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,480
but I kept feeling like you were coming for me,

70
00:06:07,879 --> 00:06:09,439
so I spruced myself up a bit.

71
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,560
Where's the photo I gave you?

72
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,560
I put it away.

73
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:12,439
But yesterday,

74
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:14,120
I accidentally broke the frame.

75
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:15,079
Hope you don't mind.

76
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:19,279
I thought another woman had entered your room.

77
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:21,120
Jealousy.

78
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:23,040
Can't accept our past.

79
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:25,519
Alright.

80
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:26,480
Let's get down to business.

81
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,759
Tell me.

82
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,560
How do we collaborate?

83
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:38,439
If you can take me down,

84
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,319
we can collaborate however you want.

85
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:23,759
Have you finished reading the contract?

86
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:26,120
Drink it,

87
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,240
and I'll tell you.

88
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:44,040
Your shirt is dirty.

89
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,759
Let me help you.

90
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,040
Miss Lin,

91
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:50,560
Miss Lin,

92
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:51,959
Miss Lin,

93
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:54,000
I'm a playboy.

94
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,759
You don't need to do this for me.

95
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,759
It's okay.

96
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,279
I like it.

97
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:26,959
Oops.

98
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,759
I'm sorry.

99
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,079
Shen Shutu,

100
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:33,840
do you really think I'm so weak?

101
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,120
I have something to do.

102
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,039
I'll leave you here.

103
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,120
Take your time. Bye.

104
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,440
Shen Shutu,

105
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,559
come back here!

106
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:57,720
Come on.

107
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,759
Come on.

108
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,840
Cheers.

109
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,159
Excuse me.

110
00:09:06,279 --> 00:09:07,320
Move.

111
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,759
What are you doing?

112
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:28,840
Where's the jade pendant?

113
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:30,440
Give it to me.

114
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:30,919
Jade?

115
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:32,720
What jade pendant?

116
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:33,840
Don't play dumb.

117
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,559
Give me the jade pendant on your neck.

118
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,440
This one?

119
00:09:40,519 --> 00:09:41,600
You should have said it earlier.

120
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,600
Why bother?

121
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,200
Stop.

122
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,080
Shen Shutu.

123
00:10:16,159 --> 00:10:17,240
They're coming.

124
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,000
Go.

125
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,759
This way, hurry.

126
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:22,519
This way.

127
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:28,279
Over there, they ran over there.

128
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,200
Quick.

129
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,360
Quick.

130
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,440
Check over there.

131
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,519
Where did they go?

132
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:36,879
A small piece of paper.

133
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:37,960
A few words.

134
00:11:38,159 --> 00:11:39,279
Behind the warmth without words

135
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:41,080
is Shen Shutu's hardcore protection.

136
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,600
When the beauty comes with wine,

137
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:45,679
is it a probe or a trap?

138
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,360
Temptation and crisis

139
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:49,519
are often cloaked in a guise of gentleness.

140
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,519
The honey trap

141
00:11:50,519 --> 00:11:51,919
is not just a plot device in movies and TV shows,

142
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:52,840
but also a despicable tactic

143
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,840
used by foreign spies in reality.

144
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:55,919
In recent years,

145
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:57,639
foreign espionage and intelligence agencies

146
00:11:57,639 --> 00:12:01,000
have frequently approached personnel from key and critical departments within our country

147
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,360
in the name of exchange, research, and project collaboration,

148
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,639
seeking to

149
00:12:04,639 --> 00:12:05,679
and flatter them

150
00:12:05,679 --> 00:12:06,919
to get close to them.

151
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:10,120
Their purpose is to steal our national secrets.

152
00:12:10,519 --> 00:12:11,600
Everyone,

153
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,600
you must be highly vigilant and clear-headed,

154
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,799
recognize the spy's tricks,

155
00:12:15,799 --> 00:12:17,279
and do not lose the forest for the trees.
